  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">SUPPORT CROATIAN CHILDREN CARING FOR EACH OTHER</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We have designed 5 new workshops to address fears, in particular the fear of Covid 19, which will include children aged 7 to 14 and people with disabilities. We will include at least 25 school children from Zagreb and 25 people with intellectual disabilities of the Regoc Association from Slavonski Brod. Workshops &quot;Skillful Hands &quot; and learning how to make handicrafts from wood and fabric will alleviate the stress and fear of Covid 19, but also the fear for their loved ones.</narrative>
  </description>
